WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 26]

01:51.790 --> 01:52.930
The Dragon Deity's Power...

02:14.710 --> 02:15.530
Wu.

02:26.000 --> 02:26.650
Bai Ze?

02:40.360 --> 02:41.340
Ji Ling.

02:43.800 --> 02:45.860
You've always called me Master Dragon Deity.

02:49.400 --> 02:50.580
This is the first time

02:53.590 --> 02:54.770
you've called me by my name.

02:57.240 --> 02:58.340
I won't be able

02:59.910 --> 03:02.090
to walk this road with you to the very end.

03:05.000 --> 03:06.090
Don't be sad.

03:08.560 --> 03:10.370
There are many bright lights in this world.

03:11.680 --> 03:12.900
I only came

03:13.710 --> 03:15.250
to pass on one small flame.

03:18.000 --> 03:18.770
I'm proud

03:19.560 --> 03:20.970
to have been able to answer your questions

03:21.150 --> 03:22.210
all these years.

03:30.800 --> 03:32.580
"Records of Myriad Demons"?

03:33.800 --> 03:34.970
In this world,

03:35.560 --> 03:36.460
besides humans,

03:37.560 --> 03:39.060
there are countless demons as well.

03:45.520 --> 03:46.810
I know the workings of the world,

03:47.910 --> 03:49.810
and yet even I cannot see through the ending.

03:50.840 --> 03:51.860
You'll have to walk

03:52.800 --> 03:54.740
the road ahead alone.

03:59.750 --> 04:00.460
Bai Ze...

04:09.800 --> 04:12.090
Thank you, Bai Ze.

04:16.680 --> 04:17.770
Thank you

04:21.720 --> 04:23.660
for everything you did for me.

04:27.260 --> 04:34.580
♪So many lives, like a speck of dust♪

04:34.980 --> 04:41.220
♪Yet every tiny me speaks loud and just♪

05:05.630 --> 05:06.690
Lonescale,

05:09.680 --> 05:10.570
it's you.

05:35.070 --> 05:35.930
Ji Ling?

06:02.630 --> 06:04.330
She was trapped inside a lifeless object.

06:05.070 --> 06:06.620
She severed her own spiritual tail

06:06.870 --> 06:08.300
and released all her power.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.890
That was the only way she could

06:11.070 --> 06:13.010
speak faintly through the doll and stop you

06:13.680 --> 06:14.890
from killing yourself.

06:15.800 --> 06:17.330
Lu Wuyi's spiritual tail

06:17.920 --> 06:19.250
was linked to her eyesight.

06:27.070 --> 06:27.860
I'm here.

06:45.430 --> 06:46.450
Don't cry.

06:49.240 --> 06:50.330
Don't be sad.

06:52.630 --> 06:53.540
Wu

06:56.310 --> 06:57.740
will always be by your side.

07:13.800 --> 07:15.010
You silly girl.

07:43.310 --> 07:44.100
Si Feng?

07:44.870 --> 07:45.660
Hua Qi?

07:46.070 --> 07:47.010
What are you doing here?

07:54.830 --> 07:55.690
The Spirit-Binding Ring?

07:57.160 --> 07:58.980
Master Dragon Deity asked me to bring it to you.

07:59.360 --> 08:01.130
The last strand of the Dragon Deity's Power inside

08:02.240 --> 08:03.370
can help you become a dragon.

08:05.270 --> 08:06.370
The Dragon Deity's Power?

08:09.720 --> 08:10.420
Wait.

08:11.950 --> 08:14.180
Once you gain the power to kill Chi Wen,

08:15.510 --> 08:16.540
Jiu Ying will...

08:19.270 --> 08:20.370
You have no choice.

08:38.510 --> 08:39.540
Wu Wangyan,

08:40.240 --> 08:42.020
it's time you played your part.

08:48.200 --> 08:49.140
Take Wangyan and go!

08:53.320 --> 08:54.140
- Let's go. - Watch out!

09:52.150 --> 09:52.930
Wu Wangyan!

09:53.510 --> 09:54.020
Wangyan.

09:56.960 --> 09:57.500
Wangyan?

09:59.360 --> 10:00.420
Use your death

10:01.000 --> 10:02.610
to shatter his mind.

10:03.320 --> 10:03.850
Wangyan,

10:04.390 --> 10:05.140
hang in there.

10:05.720 --> 10:06.730
You'll be all right.

10:07.030 --> 10:07.690
Wangyan!

10:10.030 --> 10:10.610
Wangyan.

10:11.510 --> 10:12.180
Wu Wangyan!

10:12.480 --> 10:14.570
You swore you would protect her.

10:14.960 --> 10:15.850
And what happened?

10:16.630 --> 10:18.140
You can't protect anyone.

10:18.390 --> 10:19.300
Don't listen to her.

10:20.480 --> 10:21.730
Don't listen to her.

10:25.200 --> 10:26.020
Calm down.

10:26.240 --> 10:27.850
Wu Shiguang, calm down.

10:28.510 --> 10:29.090
Hua Qi,

10:29.480 --> 10:30.060
help me.

10:30.630 --> 10:31.570
Take her

10:31.720 --> 10:32.730
to the Formless Moon!

10:34.440 --> 10:35.020
Wangyan.

10:58.910 --> 11:00.090
Finally.

11:08.550 --> 11:09.330
Wu Shiguang!

11:10.750 --> 11:11.540
Wu Shiguang!

11:13.550 --> 11:14.810
Wu Shiguang!

11:28.480 --> 11:29.090
Wu Shiguang.

11:30.320 --> 11:30.970
Wu Shiguang!

11:32.510 --> 11:33.140
Wu Shiguang.

11:33.150 --> 11:34.190
Wake up, Wu Shiguang!

11:34.420 --> 11:35.040
Wake up!

11:35.870 --> 11:36.500
Wu Shiguang!

11:36.550 --> 11:37.420
Quiet!

11:52.480 --> 11:53.330
Chi Wen,

11:54.550 --> 11:56.140
I've come for your life.

11:57.550 --> 11:59.260
I've waited so long.

11:59.790 --> 12:00.780
This day

12:01.200 --> 12:03.020
has come after all.

12:12.030 --> 12:13.140
So only a dragon

12:14.080 --> 12:15.610
can draw the Guili Sword.

12:17.320 --> 12:18.210
Only a dragon

12:19.270 --> 12:20.730
can kill a dragon.

12:24.270 --> 12:25.380
Then I guess it's time

12:26.390 --> 12:28.090
to dot the dragon's eyes.

12:39.510 --> 12:40.500
Awake, O spirit.

12:41.120 --> 12:41.970
Return to the source!

13:23.630 --> 13:24.440
Why can't I see

13:24.440 --> 13:25.850
the memories Wu Shiguang is seeing?

13:27.120 --> 13:29.060
My fragment is clearly inside his body.

13:30.960 --> 13:32.330
What have you done?

13:33.150 --> 13:34.730
Master Dragon Deity was right.

13:35.910 --> 13:36.810
Take this

13:37.630 --> 13:38.380
to him.

13:40.840 --> 13:41.730
Inside the ring

13:42.080 --> 13:44.610
is the last strand of the Dragon Deity's Power left by Lonescale.

13:45.550 --> 13:46.420
But it also

13:46.960 --> 13:48.850
carries all of my memories.

13:49.270 --> 13:50.060
Then...

13:50.790 --> 13:51.730
In my memories,

13:52.270 --> 13:53.430
there is something that Jiu Ying

13:53.430 --> 13:54.540
must never see.

13:54.960 --> 13:56.420
So you must keep them away

13:56.420 --> 13:58.200
from the fragment of Jiu Ying

13:58.200 --> 13:59.060
inside Wu Shiguang.

13:59.630 --> 14:00.420
Otherwise,

14:00.840 --> 14:02.330
all our efforts will come to nothing.

14:03.200 --> 14:04.090
Only you

14:04.630 --> 14:05.730
can do this.

14:15.550 --> 14:16.810
So it's you.

14:18.150 --> 14:20.060
The bracelet I gave Wu Shiguang

14:20.600 --> 14:21.390
does contain

14:21.390 --> 14:22.550
the Eastern Purple Lightning.

14:22.550 --> 14:23.500
But while it's powerful,

14:24.000 --> 14:25.330
it lacks a guide.

14:26.270 --> 14:27.360
It can't precisely target

14:27.360 --> 14:28.200
Jiu Ying's

14:28.200 --> 14:29.610
spirit fragment inside his body.

14:30.080 --> 14:31.180
Your power, however,

14:32.360 --> 14:33.660
carries the force

14:34.120 --> 14:35.730
to purify and drive out evil.

14:37.080 --> 14:37.690
Let me do it.

14:38.440 --> 14:40.660
It will consume a vast amount of spiritual power.

14:40.840 --> 14:42.660
You only need to keep the spirit fragment away

14:42.670 --> 14:43.730
for a short while.

14:44.320 --> 14:45.060
Otherwise,

14:45.360 --> 14:46.850
your life will be in danger too.

16:00.630 --> 16:02.500
Only one head remains.

16:03.840 --> 16:04.900
Now it's my turn.

16:07.680 --> 16:08.650
Master Chi Wen,

16:10.870 --> 16:12.080
are you about to perform

16:12.080 --> 16:13.210
the Scale-Descent Rite?

16:14.080 --> 16:15.020
I...

16:15.080 --> 16:16.330
I'm ready.

16:20.270 --> 16:22.660
You think a fake Dragon Deity's bracelet

16:22.660 --> 16:23.900
can stop me?

16:24.870 --> 16:25.850
Dream on!

16:34.270 --> 16:34.970
Si Feng,

16:35.510 --> 16:36.850
since childhood, I've dreamed

16:37.480 --> 16:38.540
of becoming a double-flower hunter

16:38.750 --> 16:39.900
and fighting by your side.

16:40.550 --> 16:41.330
Now,

16:41.670 --> 16:42.690
it's finally come true.

16:43.750 --> 16:44.570
Less talking.

16:44.870 --> 16:45.660
Focus.

16:46.080 --> 16:47.300
Or you'll be wiped out body and soul.

16:50.120 --> 16:51.730
Two mere double-flower hunters

16:52.270 --> 16:53.570
dare stand in my way?

16:54.060 --> 16:56.020
♪Moon and scales shine in radiant splendor♪

16:56.220 --> 16:58.580
♪As the winds rise, dragons and foxes cry in strife♪

16:58.620 --> 17:03.020
♪At the world's end, the destined soul rides proud and free♪

17:03.340 --> 17:05.420
♪I am fearless♪

17:05.620 --> 17:07.940
♪I will gather light to mend the moon for you♪

17:08.050 --> 17:09.500
♪When heaven and earth are reborn♪

17:09.540 --> 17:12.620
♪We will meet again♪

17:12.810 --> 17:14.940
♪Moon and scales shine in radiant splendor♪

17:15.180 --> 17:17.340
♪I will gather the stars and cradle the moon for you♪

17:17.500 --> 17:19.020
♪Bearing treasured fragments of wonder♪

17:19.140 --> 17:22.980
♪Behold the moon and scales in radiant splendor♪

17:44.960 --> 17:45.650
Si Feng!

18:07.110 --> 18:07.810
Not yet,

18:07.810 --> 18:08.370
Ji Ling.

18:09.070 --> 18:10.780
After Jiu Ying's head is swallowed,

18:11.000 --> 18:12.700
someone must wield the Guili Sword

18:12.920 --> 18:14.500
and sever my dragon body

18:14.750 --> 18:16.300
to destroy Jiu Ying completely.

18:17.110 --> 18:18.300
Really?

18:19.200 --> 18:20.220
But only a dragon

18:20.550 --> 18:21.700
can kill a dragon.

18:22.510 --> 18:23.130
Ji Ling,

18:24.550 --> 18:26.500
do you know what I originally intended to do

18:27.000 --> 18:28.220
by putting my scale inside you?

18:30.310 --> 18:31.370
Master Chi Wen,

18:32.830 --> 18:33.740
I understand now.

18:35.960 --> 18:37.940
You meant to let your soul leave your body

18:38.400 --> 18:39.650
after Jiu Ying was sealed.

18:40.640 --> 18:42.060
By putting a scale in me,

18:43.590 --> 18:44.370
I

18:45.200 --> 18:46.460
would become another you.

18:48.590 --> 18:49.650
Then,

18:50.270 --> 18:51.810
I was to go to the Dragon Abyss and...

18:53.640 --> 18:55.060
Then, you were to go there

18:55.640 --> 18:56.940
and kill me.

18:57.440 --> 18:58.610
So that was the plan?

19:06.440 --> 19:08.220
But that was only the original plan.

19:09.440 --> 19:10.890
Now the plan has changed.

19:11.920 --> 19:12.850
Why?

19:15.590 --> 19:17.260
Was it...

19:19.400 --> 19:20.700
because of me?

19:25.920 --> 19:27.540
If my soul leaves my body,

19:28.160 --> 19:30.170
Jiu Ying will seize my body

19:30.590 --> 19:31.700
at once.

19:32.830 --> 19:33.740
Then what do we do?

19:34.310 --> 19:36.020
My brothers and I have created the Tenth Dragon Son

19:36.070 --> 19:37.540
using our reverse scales.

19:38.110 --> 19:39.300
You are to guide him

19:39.590 --> 19:40.740
to the Dragon Abyss

19:41.110 --> 19:42.130
and have him kill me.

19:43.880 --> 19:45.090
However, if the last dragon

19:45.790 --> 19:47.810
in this world vanishes too,

19:48.640 --> 19:50.500
people's hope will be destroyed.

19:51.790 --> 19:54.460
As fear and hatred grow,

19:54.830 --> 19:56.260
Jiu Ying's power

19:56.550 --> 19:57.780
will surge beyond control

19:58.550 --> 19:59.650
and become indestructible.

20:00.480 --> 20:01.410
So, Ji Ling,

20:03.350 --> 20:04.780
put on these clothes.

20:05.270 --> 20:06.370
From this moment on,

20:06.750 --> 20:07.330
you

20:08.160 --> 20:09.220
are me.

20:10.830 --> 20:12.610
Your duty is to leave hope in this world

20:14.440 --> 20:15.540
and leave behind something

20:16.790 --> 20:18.740
for justice and kindness to rest on,

20:21.160 --> 20:22.330
even if all of it

20:23.550 --> 20:24.850
is only an illusion.

20:34.640 --> 20:35.500
I...

20:38.350 --> 20:40.300
- Master Chi Wen, I... - From now on,

20:41.200 --> 20:42.780
you must deceive everyone,

20:44.310 --> 20:45.330
including Jiu Ying

20:45.920 --> 20:47.020
and

20:48.790 --> 20:49.780
yourself.

21:07.110 --> 21:08.570
I see.

21:12.480 --> 21:14.220
Oh, Chi Wen,

21:14.960 --> 21:17.090
what a scheme.

21:19.880 --> 21:21.890
When his mind collapses,

21:21.960 --> 21:23.700
you can seize his body,

21:24.160 --> 21:25.370
go to the Dragon Abyss,

21:25.680 --> 21:26.810
kill Chi Wen,

21:27.830 --> 21:29.850
and free your true body.

21:31.880 --> 21:32.540
Well?

21:33.160 --> 21:35.610
That fake pretended to work with me,

21:35.960 --> 21:38.370
but all he wanted was to trick me into destroying myself.

21:38.550 --> 21:40.610
Once you gather all the Dragon Deity's Power,

21:40.960 --> 21:42.850
you'll naturally understand everything.

21:44.640 --> 21:46.020
So these strands of power

21:46.020 --> 21:47.260
have been guiding me all along

21:48.830 --> 21:50.940
to fulfill my purpose as the Tenth Dragon Son.

21:52.720 --> 21:53.850
And my purpose

21:55.830 --> 21:57.060
really is to slay the dragon.

21:59.680 --> 22:00.330
Chi Wen,

22:01.590 --> 22:02.880
you've endured the agony

22:02.880 --> 22:04.410
of the Guili Sword all these years,

22:05.200 --> 22:06.220
planning every step,

22:08.550 --> 22:09.610
only to lead yourself

22:09.640 --> 22:11.020
to this fatal end,

22:12.160 --> 22:13.370
sacrifice yourself,

22:14.550 --> 22:16.090
and become the final seal.

22:18.400 --> 22:19.330
Too bad.

22:19.720 --> 22:21.780
I planted a spirit fragment in your body

22:21.780 --> 22:23.090
long ago.

22:23.790 --> 22:24.980
That fake Dragon Deity

22:25.110 --> 22:26.700
waited so long for you,

22:27.030 --> 22:29.330
and in the end, he still couldn't tell you the truth.

22:34.590 --> 22:36.370
He must have been devastated

22:36.440 --> 22:37.850
and crushed.

22:38.920 --> 22:41.370
A grand plan a century in the making,

22:41.590 --> 22:43.130
all ruined at the final moment.

22:46.440 --> 22:47.460
Everything

22:49.680 --> 22:50.890
that fake Dragon Deity did

22:52.110 --> 22:54.090
far surpassed what a real one would've done.

22:55.790 --> 22:57.170
I want him to know

22:58.680 --> 23:00.240
I refuse to go on being

23:00.240 --> 23:01.740
a Dragon Deity with no power.

23:03.920 --> 23:05.810
I want my supreme power back.

23:07.880 --> 23:10.540
I want people to worship me for generations

23:13.680 --> 23:15.130
and revere me as their god.

23:16.030 --> 23:17.130
When you said "him,"

23:18.400 --> 23:19.650
you meant Jiu Ying, right?

23:20.880 --> 23:21.700
Ji Ling

23:24.960 --> 23:27.260
should have had a life of his own.

23:28.510 --> 23:30.570
Master Chi Wen, you've given me a name,

23:31.310 --> 23:32.410
power,

23:33.000 --> 23:33.890
and even

23:34.960 --> 23:36.740
the identity of the Dragon Deity.

23:37.270 --> 23:38.350
But I've also given you

23:38.350 --> 23:39.780
eternal shackles.

23:41.240 --> 23:42.740
You'll have to live

23:44.160 --> 23:45.260
as my shadow forever.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.570
Enough.

23:56.790 --> 23:59.300
It's time to pull out that cursed Guili Sword.

23:59.640 --> 24:01.540
Hand your body over to me!

24:27.750 --> 24:28.460
Wu Shiguang!

24:29.590 --> 24:30.170
Wu Shiguang,

24:31.200 --> 24:31.940
wake up!

24:32.070 --> 24:32.650
Wu Shiguang!

24:36.960 --> 24:37.610
Wu Shiguang.

24:38.400 --> 24:39.330
Wu Shiguang, wake up!

24:39.720 --> 24:40.370
Wu Shiguang!

24:53.200 --> 24:54.020
You Chi, you...

24:54.880 --> 24:55.410
Wake up.

25:03.510 --> 25:04.170
Wu Shiguang?

25:09.680 --> 25:10.740
You overestimate yourself!

25:26.270 --> 25:27.370
Wu Shiguang, wake up!

25:28.000 --> 25:28.740
Wu Shiguang,

25:29.160 --> 25:29.810
wake up.

25:29.880 --> 25:30.850
Wu Shiguang, wake up!

25:31.160 --> 25:31.810
Wu Shiguang!

25:32.160 --> 25:32.850
Wake up.

25:33.070 --> 25:33.650
Wu Shiguang!

25:33.920 --> 25:34.700
Wu Shiguang...

25:36.350 --> 25:37.020
Wu Wangyan!

25:37.920 --> 25:38.570
Wu Shiguang.

25:38.790 --> 25:39.410
Wangyan?

25:39.680 --> 25:41.060
Thank goodness! You're alive!

25:41.240 --> 25:42.020
Wu Shiguang.

25:42.030 --> 25:42.610
Wu Shiguang!

25:42.790 --> 25:43.610
Wake up.

25:43.880 --> 25:45.090
Wake up, Wu Shiguang!

25:46.750 --> 25:47.890
Don't let Jiu Ying control you.

25:48.110 --> 25:49.020
Don't lose to him!

25:50.000 --> 25:50.810
Wu Shiguang,

25:51.240 --> 25:52.130
I'm still alive.

25:52.590 --> 25:53.370
Wu Shiguang,

25:53.440 --> 25:54.220
wake up!

25:56.590 --> 25:57.650
Wu Shiguang.

25:58.070 --> 25:59.610
Wake up, Wu Shiguang!

25:59.920 --> 26:01.850
Wu Shiguang...

26:02.310 --> 26:03.090
Wu Shiguang,

26:03.960 --> 26:04.850
I'm still alive.

26:05.000 --> 26:06.780
- Wangyan? - Wake up!

26:07.310 --> 26:09.500
Wu Shiguang, I'm alive!

26:10.240 --> 26:11.090
It's Wangyan.

26:11.440 --> 26:12.460
I'm alive.

26:12.750 --> 26:13.460
Wake up.

26:13.460 --> 26:14.220
She's all right.

26:33.960 --> 26:34.980
How laughable.

26:35.480 --> 26:36.940
You've turned yourself

26:36.940 --> 26:39.240
into something neither human nor ghost.

26:39.240 --> 26:40.320
Do you know

26:40.320 --> 26:42.170
why I made myself like this?

26:43.200 --> 26:44.410
For immortality?

26:45.480 --> 26:46.590
Too bad.

26:46.590 --> 26:47.810
You're going to die here today.

26:48.590 --> 26:51.090
It was so that even if my body perished,

26:51.720 --> 26:54.260
I could still destroy evil things like you.

27:16.920 --> 27:18.060
Si Feng, no!

27:19.270 --> 27:20.220
No!

27:23.960 --> 27:25.370
My soul I devote.

27:26.640 --> 27:28.410
Long live the dragon.

27:29.750 --> 27:30.780
Si Feng!

27:40.480 --> 27:41.500
Si Feng!

27:46.440 --> 27:47.330
Si Feng...

27:49.880 --> 27:50.610
Si Feng...

28:36.400 --> 28:37.300
My brother.

29:09.920 --> 29:10.810
My brother,

29:11.400 --> 29:13.370
people worship the Dragon Deity.

29:13.790 --> 29:15.200
They carve the dragon's image

29:15.200 --> 29:16.740
into palaces and temples,

29:17.200 --> 29:19.300
and embroider it into splendid robes.

29:20.160 --> 29:21.650
They revere us.

29:22.030 --> 29:23.090
They adore us.

29:23.400 --> 29:25.330
That gives us power,

29:25.920 --> 29:27.610
but it also gives us responsibility.

29:28.640 --> 29:30.570
Even if this body of mine falls,

29:30.880 --> 29:33.610
the dragon's soul will endure forever

29:33.960 --> 29:36.170
to protect all living beings.

29:43.400 --> 29:44.260
Jiu Ying,

29:45.880 --> 29:47.070
all you've ever brought to the world

29:47.070 --> 29:50.020
is hatred and fear.

29:51.920 --> 29:53.370
You will never understand

29:56.830 --> 29:58.300
what it means to protect.

30:00.020 --> 30:01.380
♪Strike...♪

30:01.680 --> 30:02.540
Let scales rise,

30:03.270 --> 30:04.570
blessing all living things.

30:04.700 --> 30:07.420
♪Across the sacred peaks, we wipe out every evil...♪

30:08.960 --> 30:09.780
Let claws grow,

30:10.200 --> 30:11.410
sweeping away evil.

30:13.020 --> 30:15.820
♪All ranks advance in formation♪

30:15.860 --> 30:18.660
♪With a blazing sun within, all souls are divine...♪

30:18.960 --> 30:19.850
Let horns rise,

30:20.960 --> 30:22.130
sheltering the world.

30:22.940 --> 30:26.220
♪In this black-and-white game, each move is made without regret♪

30:26.700 --> 30:29.580
♪Whom does this dazzling sea of flowers bury?♪

30:30.020 --> 30:31.060
♪Right and wrong, cause and consequence♪

30:31.140 --> 30:35.420
♪Regret and wasted years consume me as karmic fire rages on...♪

30:36.030 --> 30:36.890
Let eyes open,

30:39.160 --> 30:40.570
unleashing dragon's might.

30:43.880 --> 30:45.170
Let the dragon's roar rise from my heart,

30:46.110 --> 30:47.330
Let scales bloom in all directions!

30:48.790 --> 30:49.740
A six-flower mark?

30:55.340 --> 30:57.220
♪Let the heavy snow fall♪

30:57.300 --> 31:00.620
♪I will not kneel, bow, or beg for release♪

31:01.300 --> 31:03.300
♪Oh, the scars of this life♪

31:03.500 --> 31:04.340
♪I embrace the moonlight♪

31:04.340 --> 31:07.260
♪I embrace the shackles...♪

31:08.070 --> 31:09.780
I will fulfill the final wish my brothers

31:11.720 --> 31:12.740
left behind.

31:15.180 --> 31:16.220
♪A sliver of inner darkness♪

31:16.300 --> 31:21.060
♪Love and hate tear at me as the snow cuts deep...♪

31:23.680 --> 31:24.540
Impossible!

31:24.830 --> 31:26.020
I won't die!

31:26.510 --> 31:29.650
I refuse this fate!

31:38.920 --> 31:39.540
Wu Shiguang.

31:41.030 --> 31:41.610
Wu Shiguang?

31:43.590 --> 31:44.130
Wu Shiguang,

31:44.270 --> 31:44.890
you're back.

31:45.790 --> 31:46.850
You grew horns.

31:47.270 --> 31:48.300
You've finally become a dragon.

31:49.160 --> 31:50.020
There's a flower mark too.

31:50.200 --> 31:52.850
One, two, three, four,

31:53.720 --> 31:54.260
five.

31:55.550 --> 31:57.260
You're a one-of-a-kind five-flower hunter!

31:58.750 --> 31:59.850
Count again.

32:01.880 --> 32:03.170
That's a six-flower mark.

32:32.030 --> 32:32.980
Wu Shiguang.

32:38.030 --> 32:38.810
I thought

32:42.200 --> 32:43.300
I'd lost you.

33:12.070 --> 33:13.220
You've finally come,

33:14.510 --> 33:15.300
my little brother.

33:30.400 --> 33:31.130
Shiguang,

33:33.000 --> 33:34.330
you've finally become a dragon.

33:36.160 --> 33:36.960
You now have

33:36.960 --> 33:38.700
your own Dragon Deity's Power.

33:41.000 --> 33:41.980
Do it.

33:43.510 --> 33:44.980
Put an end to all of this.

34:42.110 --> 34:43.210
Don't be sad.

34:43.710 --> 34:45.460
After we're gone,

34:46.110 --> 34:48.570
you'll still have someone important by your side,

34:48.840 --> 34:50.610
walking beside you.

34:51.440 --> 34:53.020
The mountains stand with you too,

34:54.150 --> 34:56.290
keeping you company.

35:03.480 --> 35:04.540
Don't be sad.

35:07.150 --> 35:08.420
I know Si Feng.

35:09.800 --> 35:11.290
She died with no regrets,

35:13.070 --> 35:13.860
because

35:16.590 --> 35:17.820
she protected

35:19.070 --> 35:20.770
the one she wanted to protect.

35:23.110 --> 35:23.980
I know.

35:26.320 --> 35:27.570
She always said

35:29.320 --> 35:31.020
you were her only demon friend.

35:31.920 --> 35:32.460
No.

35:34.510 --> 35:35.900
The one she wanted to protect

35:36.760 --> 35:37.940
was always you.

35:42.320 --> 35:44.210
I hope Han Ba will keep his promise and come

35:44.480 --> 35:45.730
to the Shilin Sect to face judgment.

35:46.550 --> 35:47.730
Otherwise,

35:47.920 --> 35:49.690
I'll have to drag this deadweight here again

35:50.190 --> 35:51.090
to catch him myself.

35:54.800 --> 35:56.540
You're awfully good to this junior brother

35:57.320 --> 35:58.340
of yours.

35:59.320 --> 36:00.020
Am I?

36:00.840 --> 36:02.090
I find him a complete nuisance.

36:05.480 --> 36:06.460
I just hope

36:07.030 --> 36:08.070
he can become

36:08.070 --> 36:09.570
a double-flower hunter soon.

36:10.590 --> 36:11.460
That way,

36:12.440 --> 36:14.340
I won't have to protect him all the time.

36:16.960 --> 36:18.090
But you look

36:18.480 --> 36:19.570
pretty happy doing it.

36:20.300 --> 36:24.940
♪Red-rimmed eyes hide so many unsaid...♪

36:24.960 --> 36:26.500
I grew up an orphan.

36:27.000 --> 36:27.940
I never had any family.

36:28.920 --> 36:30.290
He's like a little brother to me.

36:31.880 --> 36:34.020
You owe me a favor, don't you?

36:38.150 --> 36:39.980
If I'm gone one day,

36:46.110 --> 36:47.650
take good care of him for me.

36:55.840 --> 36:57.290
Si Feng had no regrets.

36:58.030 --> 36:59.090
You shouldn't have any either.

37:00.030 --> 37:01.210
Your magic

37:02.440 --> 37:03.860
can protect people

37:04.840 --> 37:06.020
and save people.

37:07.320 --> 37:08.650
We all need you.

37:12.880 --> 37:13.820
I will

37:15.000 --> 37:17.250
become a great hero like her.

37:19.070 --> 37:19.980
Si Feng,

37:21.030 --> 37:22.170
I will.

37:24.480 --> 37:25.820
I promise.

37:34.920 --> 37:35.940
Where do we go next?

37:36.550 --> 37:37.420
Back to the Shilin Sect?

37:49.110 --> 37:50.060
To the Formless Moon.

37:51.070 --> 37:52.250
The last fragment

37:52.800 --> 37:54.730
of Jiu Ying's spirit is still inside Lu Wuyi.

37:55.480 --> 37:56.770
All the spirit fragments

37:57.440 --> 37:59.860
rely on the divine power of the Oracle Stone to survive.

38:00.630 --> 38:01.940
Only by destroying the Oracle Stone

38:02.880 --> 38:04.540
can we kill Jiu Ying for good.

38:20.190 --> 38:21.160
"The old dragon falls.

38:22.070 --> 38:23.090
The new dragon rises.

38:24.000 --> 38:24.980
Heaven and earth tremble.

38:25.400 --> 38:26.380
Chaos fills the world.

38:28.590 --> 38:30.210
An old soul returns against time.

38:30.760 --> 38:33.020
A new moon reshapes the world."

38:33.630 --> 38:34.820
Why would a new dragon

38:36.150 --> 38:37.500
bring chaos to the world?

38:38.280 --> 38:39.170
What does it mean?

38:41.030 --> 38:42.610
The new prophecy has already descended.

38:43.440 --> 38:45.170
Why isn't the Fox Queen here?

38:45.170 --> 38:46.360
[The old dragon falls. The new dragon rises.]

38:46.360 --> 38:47.460
[Heaven and earth tremble. Chaos fills the world.]

38:47.460 --> 38:49.060
[An old soul returns against time. A new moon reshapes the world.]

41:04.960 --> 41:07.020
Before, I fell asleep in the main hall too.

41:08.630 --> 41:09.820
Now that I think about it,

41:12.030 --> 41:14.020
it really was you who carried me back to my room.

41:14.920 --> 41:15.650
It was.

41:17.230 --> 41:18.860
And you kept drawing mustaches

41:19.150 --> 41:20.060
on my statue.

41:42.710 --> 41:44.380
After everything that's happened,

41:45.710 --> 41:46.650
it feels

41:47.360 --> 41:49.170
like everything has come full circle.

41:52.030 --> 41:53.650
As long as you're still by my side,

41:55.070 --> 41:56.380
no matter what time we return to

41:57.920 --> 41:59.020
or what we return as,

41:59.960 --> 42:01.060
I'll be content.

42:16.630 --> 42:17.650
Flowers?

42:32.920 --> 42:33.730
They smell so nice.

42:36.550 --> 42:38.020
You picked flowers for me again?

42:44.280 --> 42:45.380
Too bad you'll never

42:49.510 --> 42:51.570
be able to see these beautiful flowers again.

42:53.800 --> 42:55.610
Even if the moon cannot be seen,

42:56.800 --> 42:58.170
those who care for it

42:58.590 --> 43:00.380
will still keep looking up.

43:01.510 --> 43:03.460
Even if we cannot grow old together,

43:05.190 --> 43:07.060
we can still be like two distant mountains

43:07.840 --> 43:09.090
waiting for a snowfall,

43:11.670 --> 43:12.650
just like...

43:13.110 --> 43:14.940
Just like when I was haunted by my inner demon.

43:15.710 --> 43:17.250
Even when I couldn't see you,

43:17.840 --> 43:19.460
you were still by my side,

43:20.880 --> 43:21.730
keeping me company

43:23.590 --> 43:24.540
and saving me.

43:27.500 --> 43:32.540
♪They say if we loved once before♪

43:33.540 --> 43:36.380
♪Even apart, we still feel it all♪

43:37.060 --> 43:43.740
♪Like thousands of blooms on that shore♪

43:45.700 --> 43:49.900
♪At last, the moment is here♪

43:50.700 --> 43:57.380
♪You smile at me, but it's bittersweet♪

43:57.700 --> 44:01.780
♪Hand in hand, we walk side by side♪

45:04.100 --> 45:05.260
♪It's your light♪

45:05.460 --> 45:07.340
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

45:07.500 --> 45:10.620
♪That set the night alight♪

45:10.980 --> 45:17.500
♪And lead me through the fight♪

45:19.260 --> 45:21.140
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

45:21.580 --> 45:26.020
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

45:26.820 --> 45:28.500
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

45:28.660 --> 45:34.060
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

45:34.820 --> 45:40.220
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

45:42.540 --> 45:48.580
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

45:49.540 --> 45:51.700
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

45:51.980 --> 45:56.820
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

45:57.180 --> 45:59.500
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

45:59.700 --> 46:04.780
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

46:05.020 --> 46:07.020
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

46:07.300 --> 46:11.660
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

46:12.660 --> 46:19.620
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

46:36.180 --> 46:39.140
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

46:40.220 --> 46:43.620
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

46:44.420 --> 46:46.940
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

46:47.180 --> 46:50.260
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

46:50.660 --> 46:52.980
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

46:53.500 --> 46:57.900
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

46:58.140 --> 47:00.300
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

47:00.700 --> 47:05.660
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

47:05.900 --> 47:07.060
♪It's your light♪

47:07.260 --> 47:09.100
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

47:09.300 --> 47:12.420
♪That set the night alight♪

47:13.180 --> 47:22.620
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
